{"title":"要编诗歌飞满天","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"要编诗歌飞满天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电灯开关放光明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线照亮我的眼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼中看来心里想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要编诗歌飞满天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘古初分到如今，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未见农民当诗人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国兴起共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民作者集成群。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱歌本从劳动起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动越好歌越多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种田要用好锄头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱歌要用好歌手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今歌手人人是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱得长江水倒流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要写诗篇不太难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打破迷信是关键，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众智慧发动起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能写诗歌万万篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多多的编，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多多的唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱得人人争上游，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱得红旗遍地插。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}